<h4>Our Global Shamanic Community is organized into five regional groups within the US with additional communities in Canada and Peru. Our community members, practitioners of the Pachakuti Mesa Tradition Shamanic Arts, gather for seasonal Earth honoring ceremonies and Full/New Moon Ceremonies as well as pilgrimages to sacred sites. Additionally, If you are interested in learning more about the Pachakuti Mesa Tradition we encourage you to contact your regional community members and attend a gathering or workshop in your area.</h4>
